README

Universita` di Trento, corso di Ingegneria del software, a.a. 2011/12, gruppo Orbit

== Run ==
- Install play (http://www.playframework.org/)
- copy orbit/conf/application.conf.template to orbit/conf/application.conf
- edit orbit/conf/application.conf to your needs

=== Using mysql ===
Mysql is the defautl database engine. if you don't change this setting in
orbit/conf/application.conf, you will need a mysql database running and:
- Put (or symlink) the java mysql connector in orbit/lib
- create an empty database:
  CREATE DATABASE phdcoursedb CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci;

== Build javadoc ==
If an sh compliant shell is available in your system, simply run:
sh orbit/docs/makedoc.sh
Otherways, open the script and call an analoguos command, as it is available
on your system.
